description:
Wes Peppers continues his exploration into the sanctuary by explaining the spiritual meaning of the tabernacle. There is a reason why God gave detailed instructions to Moses for building the Sanctuary. Each piece of furniture had very specific details and Wes Peppers shares how each piece of furniture has a practical application for our everyday Christian lives. He also presents how we go through a specific, step by step, process of salvation which is outlined in the Old Testament Sanctuary. Learn how to follow the plan of salvation in your life.

For more, please visit:
https://amazingdiscoveries.org
https://amazingdiscoveries.tv
